cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.NE 

This paper deals with reinforcement learning in a first-person shooter environment, using deep neural networks and ensembling techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CV (Computer Vision) due to the use of image-based input. The paper also deals with robotics (cs.RO) as the ViZDoom environment simulates combat scenarios, and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) due to the use of deep neural networks.
